## Growing and Developing with the Community

The Company aspires to Improve the competence and independence  of the community  in  the economic  field. On  that basis, the Company carries out Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR) activities  that  provides  direct  benefits  for  the community.

The  Company  held  the  2023  Festival  Hijriah in  nine  cities  in  Java  in  collaboration  with  the Indonesian Chamber of Commerce and Industry and  the  China  Committee.  An  arts  and  cultural performance featuring artists from Xinjiang was held from Jakarta to Surabaya. The festival was unique because it was the first time that it hosted an international performance by entertainers from Muslim Xinjiang,  which  originated  in  China.  The entertainers  performed  Xinjiang  art  to  entertain the  Indonesian  people  while  also  conveying  the message  of  harmonious  life  between  Muslims and Chinese.

In addition to the Xinjiang art performances, the festival also featured MSMEs from the cities where it was held. The festival helped to build the Islamic

